01:02:01,343 --> 01:02:03,387
- 你还好吗？  - 还好
- You okay?     - Yeah.

747
01:02:03,470 --> 01:02:04,805
这太疯狂了
It was crazy.

748
01:02:08,809 --> 01:02:10,811
对不起之前我不相信你
I'm sorry I didn't believe you before.

749
01:02:10,894 --> 01:02:12,396
现在我信了
Now I get it.

750
01:02:14,314 --> 01:02:15,649
还有…
And...

751
01:02:16,984 --> 01:02:19,403
当时我昏倒了
And I must have passed out,

752
01:02:20,279 --> 01:02:21,655
接着你就出现
and then you showed up.

753
01:02:22,573 --> 01:02:24,116
听着
Listen,

754
01:02:24,199 --> 01:02:27,703
我知道我总是那个要被依赖的人
I know I've always been the one who needed you

755
01:02:27,786 --> 01:02:29,121
比起你依赖我来
more than you needed me.

756
01:02:29,204 --> 01:02:30,748
- 不是真的  - 是真的
- That's not true. - Yes, it is,

757
01:02:30,831 --> 01:02:32,332
但我不在乎
but I never cared.

758
01:02:39,548 --> 01:02:42,676
我只有妈妈，卢克和你了
I've only ever had my mom, Luke and you.

759
01:02:43,427 --> 01:02:46,430
别乱想你对我来说不重要
Don't ever imagine that you weren't important to me.

760
01:02:47,514 --> 01:02:49,099
- 好吧  - 好吧
- Okay.   - Okay.

761
01:03:32,601 --> 01:03:34,603
你跟钢琴有仇吗？
What did that piano ever do to you?

762
01:03:34,686 --> 01:03:37,064
好像失去唯一真爱一样
You play it like you've lost your only love.

763
01:03:37,439 --> 01:03:39,817
不幸的是我唯一真爱就是自己
Unfortunately, my one true love remains myself.

764
01:03:39,900 --> 01:03:41,652
至少你不用愁遭拒绝
Well, at least you don't have to worry about rejection.

765
01:03:41,735 --> 01:03:42,591
那也不一定
Not necessarily.

766
01:03:42,591 --> 01:03:45,614
我有时会自我分裂，寻求刺激
I turn myself down occasionally just to keep it interesting.

767
01:03:45,906 --> 01:03:47,658
你弹得很有热情
You do play that with a lot of passion.

768
01:03:47,741 --> 01:03:48,919
这才有问题
Well, that's the problem.

769
01:03:48,919 --> 01:03:50,369
我不该投入太多感情
I play it with too much emotion.

770
01:03:50,452 --> 01:03:53,696
本应该只是简单地音符重现
It's supposed to be played with a simple representation of notes,

771
01:03:53,696 --> 01:03:54,581
而不是诠释
no interpretation.

772
01:03:58,210 --> 01:04:00,754
音乐就该有感情
Music is supposed to have emotion.

773
01:04:03,423 --> 01:04:06,844
邪灵对交错的音调才有反应
Demons react to certain frequencies when two tones cross.

774
01:04:07,928 --> 01:04:09,137
才能使他们癫狂
Drives them crazy.

775
01:04:12,432 --> 01:04:15,310
看，巴赫发现这点并构建了一个体系
See, Bach discovered this and put it into a system using

776
01:04:15,394 --> 01:04:18,188
用数字序列融合音调
a mathematical progression of tonal combinations

777
01:04:18,272 --> 01:04:20,107
