抱歉忘记告诉你会定时喷水
Sorry about the sprinkler system.

858
01:10:40,362 --> 01:10:41,655
别提它了
I forgot about that.

859
01:10:45,075 --> 01:10:46,284
要去睡了吗？
You going to sleep?

860
01:10:46,368 --> 01:10:47,827
累了吗？
Well, aren't you tired?

861
01:10:48,286 --> 01:10:49,996
我从没这样清醒
I've never been more awake.

862
01:10:56,127 --> 01:10:58,171
- 西蒙，我以为你…  - 睡了？
- Simon, I thought you were... - Asleep?

863
01:10:58,338 --> 01:10:59,506
之前是的
Yeah, I was.

864
01:10:59,923 --> 01:11:01,132
我们只不过…
We were just...

865
01:11:01,216 --> 01:11:02,658
下次，最好是
Next time, it might be a nice idea

866
01:11:02,658 --> 01:11:04,761
你得说你已经有个男人在床上
to mention that you already have a man in your bed,

867
01:11:04,844 --> 01:11:06,513
我们才不会这么尴尬了
so we can avoid such uncomfortable situations.

868
01:11:06,596 --> 01:11:07,558
你让他到你床上？
You invited him to bed?

869
01:11:07,558 --> 01:11:08,890
我知道这挺荒唐的，是不是？
I know, it's ridiculous, isn't it?

870
01:11:08,974 --> 01:11:10,183
不可能一切合心意
We would never have all fit.

871
01:11:10,267 --> 01:11:12,143
我没有让他到我床上
I didn't invite him into bed.

872
01:11:12,227 --> 01:11:14,020
只是接吻而已
We were just kissing.

873
01:11:15,480 --> 01:11:17,274
你太快丢掉我俩的爱了
How swiftly you dismiss our love.

874
01:11:17,691 --> 01:11:18,858
杰斯…
Jace...

875
01:11:19,025 --> 01:11:20,652
西蒙，很晚了，对不起吵醒你
Simon, it's late, and I'm sorry we woke you.

876
01:11:20,735 --> 01:11:22,028
我也是
So am I.

877
01:11:24,030 --> 01:11:26,511
去吧，去找他，去向他道歉
Go ahead. Go after him, go apologize to him,

878
01:11:26,511 --> 01:11:28,827
去跟他说他才是特别的
go tell him just how special he really is.

879
01:11:28,910 --> 01:11:30,745
- 别这样！  - 哪样了？
- Stop acting like that! - Like what?

880
01:11:30,829 --> 01:11:32,151
好像你没受伤一样
Like nothing ever hurts you.

881
01:11:32,151 --> 01:11:34,494
嗯，也许你应该想清楚的
Well, maybe you should have thought about that

882
01:11:34,494 --> 01:11:35,542
在你亲我之前
before you kissed me.

883
