是我亲你？
I kissed you?

884
01:11:37,711 --> 01:11:40,380
别担心，这对我也没什么了不起
Don't worry, it wasn't that special for me either.

885
01:11:45,719 --> 01:11:48,138
西蒙，真的很抱歉，我还以为你在…
I'm really sorry, Simon, but weren't you just in the...

886
01:11:48,221 --> 01:11:49,889
