- 你要去哪儿？  - 回家
- Where are you going? - Home.

888
01:11:52,392 --> 01:11:54,227
显然我在这太久，不受欢迎了
It's clear I overstayed my welcome.

889
01:11:54,311 --> 01:11:56,604
对不起，这对我也太突然了
Look, I'm sorry, okay? It wasn't like it was planned.

890
01:11:56,688 --> 01:11:59,232
但就是发生了，拜托
Let me guess, it just happened. Please.

891
01:11:59,316 --> 01:12:00,984
听着，我知道你不喜欢他，但是…
Look, I know you don't like him, but...

892
01:12:01,067 --> 01:12:03,236
其实我恨他
Actually, I hate the guy.

893
01:12:03,570 --> 01:12:04,738
为什么？
Why?

894
01:12:04,821 --> 01:12:06,114
我以为你不至于爱上他
I thought you were better than that.

895
01:12:06,197 --> 01:12:07,949
那这又说明什么？
What's that supposed to mean?

896
01:12:08,074 --> 01:12:11,369
我才是一直等你的人，不是他
I'm the one who's always been there for you, not him.

897
01:12:20,754 --> 01:12:22,547
我早爱上你了
I'm in love with you.

898
01:12:32,974 --> 01:12:35,977
不过显然你没有同感
And it's clear that you don't feel the same way.

899
01:12:37,937 --> 01:12:39,272
- 这…  - 不
- It's... - Don't.

900
01:12:39,647 --> 01:12:41,483
没什么好说了
There's nothing to say.

901
01:12:44,986 --> 01:12:46,488
还有，克拉蕾
And, Clary,

902
01:12:46,571 --> 01:12:48,740
他只是利用你获得圣杯
he's just using you to get the Cup.

903
01:12:54,621 --> 01:12:55,997
西蒙…
Simon...

904
01:14:50,403 --> 01:14:53,490
你母亲也能这么做
Your mother was the only other person who could do that.

905
01:14:54,115 --> 01:14:56,409
但我之前从没这么做过
But I've never been able to do this before.

906
01:14:57,202 --> 01:15:00,663
说明封印住的不仅是你的回忆
Apparently the block wasn't just repressing your memories,

907
01:15:00,747 --> 01:15:02,624
还有你的能力
but your abilities as well.

908
01:15:23,102 --> 01:15:25,063
- 杰斯，我…  - 别跟我说
- Jace, I... - Don't tell me.

909
01:15:25,146 --> 01:15:27,815
你急需一个裸模来画画
You have a drawing emergency and you need a nude model.

910
01:15:27,899 --> 01:15:30,151
