- I'm not in the mood. - Listen!

911
01:15:30,777 --> 01:15:33,112
我知道我妈妈将圣杯藏哪儿了
I know where my mom hid the Cup.

912
01:15:46,292 --> 01:15:47,377
克拉蕾…
Clary...

913
01:15:47,460 --> 01:15:49,420
你看上去很不同
Wow, you look different.

914
