Stop!

935
01:19:12,457 --> 01:19:13,750
拿来看看
Let's have a look.

936
01:20:03,549 --> 01:20:04,550
快跑！
Get out!

937
01:20:36,749 --> 01:20:38,322
你好，多萝西夫人
Hey, Madame Dorothea.

938
01:20:38,322 --> 01:20:39,752
有看见克拉蕾吗？
Have you seen Clary?

939
01:20:39,836 --> 01:20:41,671
我刚收到短信说她在这儿
I just got a text that said she was here.

940
01:20:41,754 --> 01:20:43,005
没有
No.

941
01:20:43,089 --> 01:20:44,924
好吧，我只是…
Okay. Well, I'll just...

942
01:20:45,091 --> 01:20:46,509
西蒙！
Simon!

943
01:20:47,426 --> 01:20:48,928
西蒙！
Simon!

944
01:20:49,720 --> 01:20:51,013
西蒙！
Simon!

945
01:20:51,097 --> 01:20:53,099
西蒙，这不是真的她！
Simon, it's not really her!

946
01:20:54,684 --> 01:20:55,685
西蒙！
Simon!

947
01:20:56,727 --> 01:20:58,104
西蒙！
Simon!

948
01:21:03,359 --> 01:21:04,777
我来照顾他
I'll take care of him.

949
01:21:05,903 --> 01:21:06,946
西蒙！
Simon!

950
01:21:07,029 --> 01:21:08,906
她拿走了圣杯！
She's got the Cup!

951
01:21:22,753 --> 01:21:23,921
西蒙！
Simon!

952
01:22:10,468 --> 01:22:11,636
对不起
I'm sorry.

953
01:22:11,719 --> 01:22:13,429
对不起
I'm sorry.

954
01:22:25,524 --> 01:22:27,026
杰斯！
Jace!

955
01:22:31,197 --> 01:22:33,199
图符不起作用
The runes aren't working.

956
01:22:39,038 --> 01:22:40,831
西蒙，跟着我
Simon, you follow me.

957
01:22:49,215 --> 01:22:50,549
把他们切碎
You cut these up.

958
01:22:53,260 --> 01:22:54,409
不要 够了
Don't. You've done enough.

959
01:22:54,409 --> 01:22:56,472
别这样对她 这不是她的错
Don't talk to her like that. This isn't her fault.

960
01:22:56,555 --> 01:22:58,432
- 不，你说的对，是你的错  - 伊莎贝尔！
- No, you're right. This is your fault. - Isabelle!

961
01:22:58,516 --> 01:23:00,393
亚力克一直都告诫你你会受伤
Alec kept telling you that you were going to get hurt.

962
01:23:00,476 --> 01:23:02,288
你会让我们都受伤
You were going to get us all hurt.

963
01:23:02,288 --> 01:23:03,479
现在他却快死了
Now he's the one dying.

964
01:23:03,562 --> 01:23:04,939
我们需要找到圣杯
Well, we needed to get the Mortal Cup.

965
01:23:05,022 --> 01:23:06,461
但还有别的办法
But there were other ways to do it

966
01:23:06,461 --> 01:23:07,984
没必要为此伤害你的挚友
than getting your best friend killed.

967
01:23:10,361 --> 01:23:11,904
去找霍奇
Why don't you go get Hodge.

968
01:23:13,364 --> 01:23:15,241
我从没想让亚力克这样
I never wanted anything to happen to Alec.

969
01:23:15,324 --> 01:23:16,742
对不起
I'm sorry.

970
01:23:21,414 --> 01:23:24,208
我们同意一起做的，我们一个团队
We agreed to do this together. We're a team.

971
01:23:24,291 --> 01:23:26,711
有了克拉蕾，我们就不是一个团队了
Since Clary got here, we haven't been a team.

972
01:23:31,424 --> 01:23:32,717
霍奇
Hodge!

973
01:23:33,259 --> 01:23:34,677
霍奇
Hodge!

974
01:23:35,553 --> 01:23:37,013
亚力克受伤了
Alec's getting worse.

975
01:23:37,096 --> 01:23:38,264
我知道
I know.

976
01:23:39,348 --> 01:23:41,308
我已经叫人来了
I've already sent for someone.

977
01:23:42,935 --> 01:23:44,729
你得到圣杯了吗？
Did you get the Cup?

978
01:24:08,294 --> 01:24:09,795
然后呢？
What now?

979
01:24:14,800 --> 01:24:16,093
霍奇？
Hodge?

980
01:24:22,516 --> 01:24:25,061
你根本不知道
You have no idea what it's like

981
01:24:25,144 --> 01:24:27,646
克拉夫的诅咒是什么滋味
living with the Clave's curse,

982
01:24:27,730 --> 01:24:30,483
不能从这儿踏出一步
unable to set so much as a foot outside,

983
01:24:31,358 --> 01:24:33,819
连开窗户都害怕
afraid to even open a window.

984
01:24:36,655 --> 01:24:38,741
克拉蕾，别太怪我
Try not to judge me too harshly, Clary.

985
01:24:48,709 --> 01:24:50,169
霍奇，你要做什么？
Hodge, what have you done?

986
01:25:13,984 --> 01:25:16,278
我知道你终将把圣杯给我
I always knew you would bring me the Cup.

987
01:25:16,362 --> 01:25:18,114
只是时间问题而已
It was only a matter of time.

988
01:25:21,367 --> 01:25:22,993
我妈妈在哪儿？
Where is she?

989
01:25:24,703 --> 01:25:25,955
她很好
She's fine.

990
01:25:30,167 --> 01:25:32,169
你得到了想要的，现在放她走
You got what you want. Now let her go.

991
01:25:32,253 --> 01:25:34,839
我得看看这是不是真的
I have to make sure you gave me the real one.

992
01:25:37,383 --> 01:25:39,885
每个人为了圣杯都会不择手段
Everybody wants the Cup for the wrong reason.

993
01:25:42,638 --> 01:25:43,973
那你没有吗？
And you don't?

994
01:25:44,056 --> 01:25:45,432
拥有它
With this Cup,

995
01:25:45,516 --> 01:25:48,144
我才能净化我的血统
I can cleanse our bloodlines,

996
01:25:48,227 --> 01:25:50,312
拯救我们的种族
Save our race.

997
01:25:50,396 --> 01:25:53,983
你也许不太了解人类历史
You might not know much about mundane history,

998
01:25:54,066 --> 01:25:58,002
听着，当人们谈论保护种族时
but I can tell you when people start talking about preserving a race,

999
01:25:58,002 --> 01:25:59,071
从没好事发生
it never goes well.

1000
01:26:00,739 --> 01:26:03,909
这就是为何我妈妈要用一生时间隐瞒你
That's why my mom spent her whole life hiding it from you.

1001
01:26:03,993 --> 01:26:05,244
不
No.

1002
01:26:06,579 --> 01:26:08,581
她不是要藏圣杯
She wasn't hiding the Cup.

1003
01:26:09,081 --> 01:26:10,833
她是要藏着你
She was hiding you.

1004
01:26:12,918 --> 01:26:13,961
喝下去
Drink.

1005
01:26:14,044 --> 01:26:15,921
我不会喝的
I'm not gonna drink that.

1006
01:26:16,005 --> 01:26:17,423
你为什么这么害怕？
Why are you so afraid?

1007
01:26:17,548 --> 01:26:20,176
你还没出生就已经喝过它了
You've been drinking this since before you were born.

1008
01:26:20,259 --> 01:26:23,345
我在你妈妈怀孕时就给她喝过
I fed it to your mother while you were in her womb.

1009
01:26:26,015 --> 01:26:27,516
快点，克拉蕾
Come on, Clary.

1010
01:26:27,600 --> 01:26:29,351
你现在应该猜到
You must have guessed by now.

1011
01:26:29,435 --> 01:26:31,020
你所有神奇的天赋
All these amazing talents

1012
01:26:31,103 --> 01:26:33,689
都是你母亲一直想要压制的
that your mother so desperately tried to suppress,

1013
01:26:33,772 --> 01:26:35,774
你觉得它从何而来？
where do you think they came from?

1014
01:26:37,860 --> 01:26:39,612
你是我女儿
You're my daughter.

1015
01:26:40,487 --> 01:26:43,324
我的血液流淌在你的身上
My blood runs in your veins.

1016
01:26:43,908 --> 01:26:45,284
现在…
Now...

1017
01:26:46,327 --> 01:26:47,536
喝
Drink.

1018
01:26:50,664 --> 01:26:52,041
快喝！
Drink!

1019
01:27:03,135 --> 01:27:04,803
把它拿出来！
Take that out!

1020
01:27:11,518 --> 01:27:13,020
不！
No!

1021
01:27:24,990 --> 01:27:26,909
有人进入穿梭门了
Someone just went through the Portal.

1022
01:27:26,992 --> 01:27:28,661
我去看看
I'll go check.

1023
01:29:03,964 --> 01:29:04,965
抱歉
Sorry.

1024
01:29:05,049 --> 01:29:06,342
我有点太激动了
I got a bit carried away.

1025
01:29:06,425 --> 01:29:07,634
卢克，你是…
Luke, you're a...

1026
01:29:07,718 --> 01:29:10,304
克拉蕾，听我说，听着 别害怕
Clary, listen to me, listen. Don't be afraid.

1027
01:29:10,387 --> 01:29:11,722
- 听着，好吗？  - 别碰我！
- Listen, right? - Don't touch me!

1028
01:29:11,805 --> 01:29:14,308
嘿，别这样
Hey, there's no need for that.

1029
01:29:14,516 --> 01:29:16,268
那东西还会回来
That thing will be back.

1030
01:29:17,227 --> 01:29:19,229
这儿不安全
We are not safe out here.

1031
01:29:22,024 --> 01:29:24,693
我跳进穿梭门，为了躲瓦伦丁
I jumped through the Portal to get away from Valentine.

1032
01:29:25,027 --> 01:29:27,029
我以为会到我妈妈那儿
I thought I'd end up with my mom.

1033
01:29:30,866 --> 01:29:34,203
但是我却到了最不想来的地方
Instead, I ended up in the last place I wanted to be.

1034
01:29:34,620 --> 01:29:37,122
听着，穿梭门带你来
Listen, the Portal brought you here

1035
01:29:37,206 --> 01:29:39,375
说明你一定想到我了
because you must have been thinking of me.

1036
01:29:39,458 --> 01:29:41,377
你内心深处仍信任我
Deep inside, you know you can trust me.

1037
01:29:41,460 --> 01:29:42,731
你说过一点都不在乎
You said you couldn't care

1038
01:29:42,731 --> 01:29:44,380
我们发生什么事情
less what happened to either of us.

1039
01:29:44,463 --> 01:29:46,090
你跟别人一样，只是想要圣杯
You just want the Cup, like everyone else.

1040
01:29:46,173 --> 01:29:48,133
我说过要保护你，我还能怎么做？
I said that to protect you. What else could I do?

1041
01:29:48,217 --> 01:29:50,511
这次我得一直照看你
Been keeping an eye on you this whole time.

1042
01:29:58,519 --> 01:30:00,229
在旅店那儿的是你
That was you at the hotel.

1043
01:30:02,147 --> 01:30:04,066
话说投的好啊
Good throw, by the way.

1044
01:30:08,862 --> 01:30:10,030
我怎么办？
What about me?

1045
01:30:10,239 --> 01:30:11,490
你怎么办？
What about you?

1046
01:30:11,698 --> 01:30:12,866
我们说好的
We had a deal.

1047
01:30:12,950 --> 01:30:15,327
我仍然没得到圣杯，不是吗？
Well, I still don't have my Cup, do I?

1048
01:30:21,041 --> 01:30:23,252
我一直信守诺言
I held up my end of the bargain.

1049
01:30:25,003 --> 01:30:26,588
不，你没有
No, you didn't.

1050
01:30:26,672 --> 01:30:28,757
我把圣杯给你了
I gave you the Cup.

1051
01:30:28,841 --> 01:30:31,343
是你给克拉蕾的 不是我的错
You handed it to Clary. That's not my fault.

1052
01:30:31,427 --> 01:30:32,553
帮我解咒
Now lift it.

1053
01:30:34,763 --> 01:30:37,516
听着，这都是你脑子想的
Listen, it's all in your head.

1054
01:30:37,599 --> 01:30:39,351
不，不！
No. No!

1055
01:30:42,187 --> 01:30:43,897
有诅咒
There's a spell.

1056
01:30:43,981 --> 01:30:46,024
真的？诅咒？
Really? A spell?

1057
01:30:46,525 --> 01:30:49,027
这只是问题的借口
That's just an excuse for a real problem

1058
01:30:49,445 --> 01:30:50,696
在这儿
in there.

1059
01:30:52,156 --> 01:30:54,324
你以为我真的可以解决吗？
Do you really think I can fix that?

1060
01:30:54,408 --> 01:30:56,952
我给你圣杯了，你帮我带走恐惧
I give you the Cup, you take away the fear.

1061
01:31:01,707 --> 01:31:03,750
没有圣杯我也一样寸步难行
Without the Cup, I'm as stuck as you are.

1062
01:31:04,835 --> 01:31:06,712
我的恐惧才是真的
Except my fear is real.

1063
01:31:06,795 --> 01:31:08,672
每个地下生物
Every Downworlder,

1064
01:31:08,755 --> 01:31:10,507
每个守护者
every member of the Clave,

1065
01:31:10,591 --> 01:31:13,302
每个暗影猎人都在穿梭门另一侧
every Shadowhunter on both sides of the Portal

1066
01:31:13,385 --> 01:31:15,137
找我
is looking for me right now.

1067
01:31:15,220 --> 01:31:17,514
我才需要一切帮助
I'm going to need all the help I can get.

1068
01:31:17,890 --> 01:31:21,101
瓦伦丁，你不必这样的
You don't have to go through with this, Valentine.

1069
01:31:21,685 --> 01:31:24,188
邪灵从来没到过神院
A demon has never set foot in the Institute.

1070
01:31:25,898 --> 01:31:27,274
现在是时候让他们来了
Well, maybe it's time they did.

1071
01:31:30,777 --> 01:31:34,323
我等这等好多年了
I've been waiting all these years to do this.

1072
01:31:36,533 --> 01:31:38,327
我别无选择
Clary's given me no choice.

1073
01:31:41,622 --> 01:31:43,123
她会回来的
She'll come back.

1074
01:31:44,833 --> 01:31:46,043
真的吗？
Really?

1075
01:31:46,919 --> 01:31:48,420
你敢确定？
And what makes you so sure?

1076
01:31:48,504 --> 01:31:51,423
这儿有她需要的人，像她需要她妈妈一样
There's someone here she wants as much as her mother.

1077
01:31:51,924 --> 01:31:54,069
你可以骗他们
If you lie and tell them

1078
01:31:54,069 --> 01:31:56,386
说他们都是你的孩子
they're both your children,

1079
01:31:56,470 --> 01:31:58,597
你这样就能让他们心碎
you'll break their hearts.

1080
01:31:58,722 --> 01:32:00,265
那又怎么样？
What can I say?

1081
01:32:00,557 --> 01:32:02,643
心碎的人最听话
The broken make the best followers.

1082
01:32:03,310 --> 01:32:04,728
看看你
Look at you.

1083
01:32:05,437 --> 01:32:08,106
爱就是灭亡
To love is to destroy.

1084
01:33:04,246 --> 01:33:05,747
霍奇到底在哪里？
Where the hell is Hodge?

1085
01:33:05,831 --> 01:33:07,541
我们没多少时间了
We don't have much time.

1086
01:33:09,585 --> 01:33:11,795
- 这弄对了吗？  - 不
- Does this look right to you? - No.

1087
01:33:14,673 --> 01:33:15,674
快看
Hey, look.

1088
01:33:18,594 --> 01:33:20,012
马格努斯？
Magnus?

1089
01:33:22,514 --> 01:33:25,350
我需要这些，要很多
I'm going to need all of this. Lots of it.

1090
01:33:27,519 --> 01:33:28,854
拿着
Take this.

1091
01:34:02,387 --> 01:34:04,222
封锁此地
Lock this place down.

1092
01:34:04,640 --> 01:34:07,976
杀死一切异族
Those who are not allies must be killed.

1093
01:34:23,116 --> 01:34:24,993
别动 它们
Don't do that!

1094
01:34:26,662 --> 01:34:27,996
瓦伦丁
Valentine.

1095
01:34:28,747 --> 01:34:29,998
乔纳森
Jonathan.

1096
01:34:31,583 --> 01:34:33,710
你怎么知道我的真名？
How do you know my real name?

1097
01:34:34,836 --> 01:34:36,213
没人这样叫过我
Nobody calls me that.

1098
01:34:37,255 --> 01:34:38,674
是真的吗？
Is it true?

1099
01:34:40,008 --> 01:34:41,927
瓦伦丁是我父亲？
Is Valentine my father?

1100
01:34:48,350 --> 01:34:50,519
他曾是个好人
You know, he was a great man,

1101
01:34:50,602 --> 01:34:52,104
在和守护者冲突之前
until his conflict with the Clave.

1102
01:34:52,646 --> 01:34:54,356
但你妈妈偷走圣杯后
But when your mother ran away with the Cup,

1103
01:34:54,439 --> 01:34:57,609
他害怕遭守护者惩罚
he was just so afraid of retribution from the Clave,

1104
01:34:57,693 --> 01:34:59,945
他烧毁了住处
he burned their house down to the ground.

1105
01:35:02,489 --> 01:35:05,409
他要世人相信他死了
He wanted the world to believe he was dead.

1106
01:35:06,702 --> 01:35:09,538
我们在灰烬里找到一个男人
In the ashes, we found the remains of a man

1107
01:35:09,621 --> 01:35:11,707
和小孩
and a child.

1108
01:35:11,790 --> 01:35:13,458
等等，一个小孩？
Wait a second, there was a child?

1109
01:35:13,542 --> 01:35:15,627
瓦伦丁怒火中烧
Valentine was so enraged, he wanted her to believe

1110
01:35:15,711 --> 01:35:18,213
他想要她相信他和他儿子都死了
he killed himself and their son,

1111
01:35:18,922 --> 01:35:20,382
你的哥哥
your brother.

1112
01:35:21,258 --> 01:35:22,884
我有个哥哥？
I have a brother?

1113
01:35:28,181 --> 01:35:30,016
乔纳森·克里斯托弗·摩根斯坦
Jonathan Christopher Morgenstern.

1114
01:35:31,059 --> 01:35:32,644
你撒谎
You're lying.

1115
01:35:33,562 --> 01:35:35,522
我姓名是杰斯·维兰德
My name is Jace Wayland.

1116
01:35:36,481 --> 01:35:38,150
我是维兰德家族的
And my family are the Waylands.

1117
01:35:39,735 --> 01:35:43,321
你以为只有克拉蕾被封存了记忆吗？
You think Clary is the only one with a block in her mind?

1118
01:35:44,448 --> 01:35:46,241
让你看看什么是真相
Let me show you the truth.

1119
01:35:51,413 --> 01:35:53,415
你没有驯服它，你毁了它
You didn't tame him. You broke him.

1120
01:35:54,082 --> 01:35:55,751
不！你…
No! You...

1121
01:35:57,461 --> 01:35:59,463
你不是我父亲
You are not my father.

1122
01:36:00,839 --> 01:36:04,259
我来是要让你知道自己到底是谁
I came back to help you understand who you really are.

1123
01:36:06,136 --> 01:36:07,512
我懂你在这不开心
I know you're unhappy here.

1124
01:36:07,804 --> 01:36:09,431
要守很多规矩
Plagued by rules.

1125
01:36:11,057 --> 01:36:15,353
你的名字辈分仅次于我
Your place is next to me.

1126
01:36:16,313 --> 01:36:18,106
你是摩根斯坦家族一员
You're a Morgenstern.

1127
01:36:19,191 --> 01:36:20,859
你是我儿子
And you're my son.

1128
01:36:33,997 --> 01:36:35,707
我叫杰斯·维兰德
My name is Jace Wayland.

1129
01:36:39,044 --> 01:36:40,545
我是维兰德家族的
I'm a Wayland.

1130
01:36:41,588 --> 01:36:43,298
抱歉告诉你这个消息
Sorry to break this to you,

1131
01:36:43,381 --> 01:36:45,675
但也是时候该知道了
but it's time you heard the truth.

1132
01:36:45,926 --> 01:36:46,927
不
Don't.

1133
01:36:50,096 --> 01:36:52,432
只是理解方式的问题
It's all a matter of perception.

1134
01:36:54,726 --> 01:36:57,062
看到了吗？摩根斯坦
You see, Morgenstern.

1135
01:37:19,000 --> 01:37:20,377
- 拿着  - 好
- Take this. - Okay.

1136
01:37:20,836 --> 01:37:21,920
好
Okay.

1137
01:37:33,390 --> 01:37:34,641
伊莎贝尔
Isabelle.

1138
01:37:52,784 --> 01:37:53,743
克拉蕾？
Clary?

1139
01:37:53,827 --> 01:37:54,995
我们找到你妈妈了
Yeah, we found your mom.

1140
01:37:55,328 --> 01:37:56,496
他们找到她了
They found her.

1141
01:37:56,580 --> 01:37:58,456
在神院
She's at the Institute.

1142
01:38:01,960 --> 01:38:03,044
阿拉里克
Alaric.

1143
01:38:03,128 --> 01:38:05,005
我是卢克，你看到了吗？
It's Luke. Can you see it?

1144
01:38:05,505 --> 01:38:06,590
是的，我看到了
Yeah, I see it.

1145
01:38:09,092 --> 01:38:10,218
兄弟们，得走了
Hey, guys, we have to go.

1146
01:38:10,302 --> 01:38:11,803
卢克需要咱们
Luke needs us.

1147
01:38:11,887 --> 01:38:13,430
我们去哪？
Where are we headed?

1148
01:38:13,513 --> 01:38:14,556
神院
The Institute.

1149
01:38:14,806 --> 01:38:16,391
我们这是在破坏协议
We'd be breaking the accords.

1150
01:38:16,474 --> 01:38:18,268
不变身就没关系
Not if we stay human.

1151
01:38:19,019 --> 01:38:20,228
走，兄弟们！
Let's go, guys!

1152
01:38:20,312 --> 01:38:21,605
快走，快走！
Go, go, go, go!

1153
01:38:21,688 --> 01:38:22,939
快，动起来！
Come on, move it!

1154
01:38:32,240 --> 01:38:33,366
准备就绪！
Ready to go!

1155
01:38:33,450 --> 01:38:34,492
一切听指挥
They've all been briefed.

1156
01:38:34,576 --> 01:38:36,870
他是阿拉里克，我们的人
This is Alaric. He's one of us.

1157
01:38:41,583 --> 01:38:42,918
走吧
Go ahead.

1158
01:38:43,001 --> 01:38:45,670
如果需要可以将头伸出窗外
You can hang your head out the window if you need to.

1159
01:38:45,754 --> 01:38:47,672
我是狼人
I'm a werewolf

1160
01:38:47,756 --> 01:38:49,674
不是金毛犬
not a golden retriever.

1161
01:38:54,679 --> 01:38:55,847
西蒙！
Simon!

1162
01:38:59,017 --> 01:38:59,976
在这等，我会回来
Just wait here, I'll be back.

1163
01:39:00,060 --> 01:39:02,270
啥？不 伊莎贝尔，我不能…
What? No. Isabelle, I can't just...

1164
01:39:02,354 --> 01:39:04,022
不，伊莎贝尔！
No. Isabelle!

1165
01:39:08,109 --> 01:39:10,028
回来，伊莎贝尔，你去哪？
Come on, Isabelle, where are you?

1166
01:39:14,658 --> 01:39:16,451
好，上！
All right, move it!

1167
01:39:16,534 --> 01:39:18,203
快点，上！
Come on, move it!

1168
01:39:25,251 --> 01:39:26,628
好吧
All right.

1169
01:39:26,711 --> 01:39:29,214
狼人来救我们了
The werewolves are here to save us.

1170
01:39:30,006 --> 01:39:31,675
难以置信我这么说
Never thought I'd say that.

1171
01:39:37,263 --> 01:39:38,932
伊莎贝尔
Finally! Isabelle.

1172
01:39:40,934 --> 01:39:42,811
打开
Hey, open up the door.

1173
01:40:13,258 --> 01:40:15,010
起作用了
It looks like he's responding.

1174
01:40:15,093 --> 01:40:16,594
他能挺过来
He'll survive.

1175
01:40:20,515 --> 01:40:22,058
小心
And be careful.

1176
01:40:24,269 --> 01:40:26,104
有人入侵
You're being invaded.

1177
01:40:31,693 --> 01:40:33,945
召集所有邪灵…
Summoning all these bloody demons...

1178
01:41:04,642 --> 01:41:05,643
跑！
Run!

1179
01:41:14,194 --> 01:41:15,320
快跑！
Run!

1180
01:41:15,904 --> 01:41:18,323
- 走哪里？  - 那有另一个出口！
- Where are we going? - There's another exit!

1181
01:41:19,324 --> 01:41:20,867
等等
Wait.

1182
01:41:34,672 --> 01:41:36,091
伊莎贝尔！
Isabelle!

1183
01:41:37,092 --> 01:41:39,177
- 我差点杀死你了  - 是啊
- I almost killed you. - Yeah.

1184
01:41:40,178 --> 01:41:41,346
你还好吗？
You okay?

1185
01:41:41,429 --> 01:41:43,389
- 没事，我没事  - 来吧
- Yeah, yeah. I'm fine. - Come on.

1186
01:41:43,473 --> 01:41:44,766
这破地方全是邪灵
This place is full of demons.

1187
01:41:44,849 --> 01:41:46,518
这不可能
That's impossible.

1188
01:41:46,768 --> 01:41:48,228
神院是圣地
The Institute is hallowed ground.

1189
01:41:48,311 --> 01:41:50,772
他们还不知情
Yeah, no one seems to have told them that.

1190
01:41:50,855 --> 01:41:53,191
肯定有内鬼放他们进来
Someone on the inside must have let them in.

1191
01:42:00,657 --> 01:42:02,075
原是救援行动
This is a rescue mission.

1192
01:42:02,158 --> 01:42:04,244
我们可没装备作战
We are not equipped to fight demons.

1193
01:42:15,672 --> 01:42:17,423
- 分开！  - 这边！这边！
- Spread out! - That way! That way!

1194
01:42:19,634 --> 01:42:20,844
后退！快！
Move back! Come on!

1195
01:42:36,609 --> 01:42:38,236
阿拉里克，我们需要支援！
We could use some help here, Alaric!

1196
01:42:40,321 --> 01:42:41,906
阿拉里克！
Alaric!

1197
01:42:44,576 --> 01:42:46,578
振作点，这肯定还有别的出入，是吧？
Come on, there must be some other way out of here, right?

1198
01:42:46,661 --> 01:42:47,871
不，这里没有，西蒙！
No, there isn't, Simon!

1199
01:42:47,954 --> 01:42:49,122
我们撑不了多久！
We can't hold them much longer!

1200
01:43:38,463 --> 01:43:39,464
让开
Step away.

1201
01:43:41,549 --> 01:43:42,800
让开！
Step away!

1202
01:44:12,789 --> 01:44:15,750
克拉蕾，这是什么图符？
Clary, which rune is that?

1203
01:44:16,918 --> 01:44:17,919
我也不知道，它是…
I don't know, it's just...

1204
01:44:18,002 --> 01:44:19,754
- 我从没见过  - 真的吗？
- I've never seen it before. - Really?

1205
01:44:19,837 --> 01:44:21,172
不在书上
It's not in the book.

1206
01:44:24,842 --> 01:44:26,261
它在消退
It's fading.

1207
01:44:49,033 --> 01:44:50,451
肯定有地方放他们进来
Here, they're coming in through somewhere.

1208
01:44:50,535 --> 01:44:52,412
我得去阻止他们
I'm going to stop them.

1209
01:44:56,249 --> 01:44:57,500
快点
Come on.

1210
01:44:57,750 --> 01:44:58,751
你们现走
You guys go.

1211
01:44:58,918 --> 01:45:00,461
我们垫后
We'll catch up.

1212
01:45:27,822 --> 01:45:29,157
不！
No!

1213
01:45:48,426 --> 01:45:50,428
他们从屋顶下来的，跟上
They're coming from the dome. Come on.

1214
01:46:03,107 --> 01:46:04,442
乔丝琳
Jocelyn,

1215
01:46:05,485 --> 01:46:07,445
我一直惦记你
you never left my heart.

1216
01:46:07,820 --> 01:46:09,947
我现在带你回家
I've come to take you home.

1217
01:46:12,158 --> 01:46:14,535
她哪儿也不去
She's not going anywhere.

1218
01:46:16,537 --> 01:46:18,498
你怎么上来的
How did you get up here?

1219
01:46:23,878 --> 01:46:26,297
你比我想象的更强大
You're even more powerful than I anticipated.

1220
01:46:26,631 --> 01:46:28,299
离她远点
Get away from her.

1221
01:46:33,971 --> 01:46:35,223
干嘛？
What the hell?

1222
01:46:35,306 --> 01:46:37,100
听他说
Just listen to what he has to say.

1223
01:46:38,726 --> 01:46:40,686
不是你想的那样
It's not what you think.

1224
01:46:43,606 --> 01:46:44,941
终于…
Finally...

1225
01:46:46,651 --> 01:46:48,820
我的两个孩子团聚了
Both my children together.

1226
01:46:48,903 --> 01:46:51,239
我女儿
My daughter

1227
01:46:51,322 --> 01:46:52,698
和我儿子
and my son.

1228
01:46:54,283 --> 01:46:56,035
对不起，克拉蕾
I'm so sorry, Clary.

1229
01:46:57,870 --> 01:46:59,372
我原先不知道
I didn't know.

1230
01:47:00,832 --> 01:47:02,500
瓦伦丁在撒谎
Valentine's lying.

1231
01:47:02,583 --> 01:47:04,585
你是迈克尔·维兰德的儿子
You're Michael Wayland's son.

1232
01:47:04,669 --> 01:47:06,128
卢克说我哥哥已经死了
Luke said my brother is dead.

1233
01:47:06,128 --> 01:47:07,004
他死于火灾
He died in a fire,

1234
01:47:07,088 --> 01:47:09,173
他们在灰烬里找到他遗骸
and they found his remains in the ashes.

1235
01:47:09,257 --> 01:47:11,426
我带乔纳森一起逃跑的
I took Jonathan with me when I ran.

1236
01:47:11,676 --> 01:47:14,303
那孩子遗骨是狼人所为
The bones were of a child killed by wolves.

1237
01:47:17,181 --> 01:47:19,058
但愿这不是真的
I wish it wasn't true.

1238
01:47:22,019 --> 01:47:24,439
她不愿意相信
She doesn't want to believe you

1239
01:47:25,314 --> 01:47:29,277
因为她爱上你了，乔纳森
because she is in love with you, Jonathan.

1240
01:47:29,360 --> 01:47:31,654
我以为你叫杰斯
I thought your name was Jace.

1241
01:47:33,114 --> 01:47:34,866
杰斯是小名
Jace is a nickname.

1242
01:47:39,704 --> 01:47:41,581
乔纳森·克里斯托弗…
Jonathan Christopher...

1243
01:47:44,041 --> 01:47:45,334
J.C.

1244
01:47:48,254 --> 01:47:49,589
杰斯
Jace.

1245
01:48:27,502 --> 01:48:28,753
把手在这
There's the lever.

1246
01:48:28,836 --> 01:48:30,838
你进去，我阻止他们
You go close the dome and I'll hold them off.

1247
01:48:39,597 --> 01:48:41,599
把圣杯拿出来，克拉蕾
Take out the Cup, Clary.

1248
01:48:46,312 --> 01:48:47,647
拿出圣杯！
Take out my Cup!

1249
01:48:47,730 --> 01:48:49,232
我要你拿！
I want that Cup!

1250
01:48:49,315 --> 01:48:50,942
你说过不伤害她！
You said you wouldn't hurt her!

1251
01:48:53,194 --> 01:48:54,195
够了！
Enough!

1252
01:49:00,868 --> 01:49:02,036
说够了
That's enough.

1253
01:49:03,788 --> 01:49:04,872
现在！
Now!

1254
01:49:10,378 --> 01:49:11,504
卡住了！
It's stuck!

1255
01:49:11,587 --> 01:49:12,797
关掉它！
Close it!

1256
01:49:12,880 --> 01:49:14,298
不行！
I can't!

1257
01:49:15,132 --> 01:49:16,968
好像少了一块！
I think there's a piece missing!

1258
01:49:23,724 --> 01:49:24,725
克拉蕾！
Clary!

1259
01:49:44,787 --> 01:49:46,372
我非常需要它
I really need this.

1260
01:50:10,021 --> 01:50:11,188
妈妈？
Mom?

1261
01:51:07,745 --> 01:51:09,914
- 去找其他人  - 好
- Find the others. - All right.

1262
01:51:11,165 --> 01:51:15,044
好吧，你是要上还是下呢？
All right, you want to take the upstairs or the down?

1263
01:51:17,088 --> 01:51:19,715
我对底下不感冒
I'm not too crazy about the basement.

1264
01:51:25,846 --> 01:51:28,140
我撑不了太久！
I can't hold them back any longer!

1265
01:51:30,434 --> 01:51:31,936
西蒙，快点！
Simon, hurry!

1266
01:51:41,737 --> 01:51:43,364
克拉蕾！
Clary!

1267
01:51:50,287 --> 01:51:52,498
嗨，卢克先生
Hello, Mr. Garroway.

1268
01:51:52,581 --> 01:51:55,960
看起来今天你很悲剧，嗯？
Looks like you're having a rough day, eh?

1269
01:51:56,794 --> 01:52:01,424
我觉得这种情况下直接杀了你
I guess the humane thing to do in this situation

1270
01:52:01,507 --> 01:52:03,592
会仁慈点
would be to put you down.

1271
01:52:03,968 --> 01:52:05,761
你想看我变身吗？
But you wanted to see me change.

1272
01:52:06,137 --> 01:52:07,138
是的
I do.

1273
01:52:17,356 --> 01:52:18,566
起来！
Get up!

1274
01:52:20,067 --> 01:52:22,903
那么，你到底要反抗到什么时候？
So, boy, how far do you want to take this?

1275
01:52:25,406 --> 01:52:26,866
到死为止
To the end.

1276
01:52:49,430 --> 01:52:51,140
西蒙！
Simon!

1277
01:53:28,302 --> 01:53:29,845
伊莎贝尔！
Isabelle!

1278
01:53:38,854 --> 01:53:40,064
靠着我
Lean on me.

1279
01:53:57,665 --> 01:53:59,667
出去！快！
Get out! Go on!

1280
01:54:00,084 --> 01:54:01,335
离开这儿
Get out of here.

1281
01:54:04,380 --> 01:54:05,589
快跑！
Come on!

1282
01:54:09,051 --> 01:54:10,052
走！
Go!

1283
01:54:15,349 --> 01:54:17,351
听说你喜欢弹琴
Somebody told me that you like to play music.

1284
01:54:20,688 --> 01:54:22,398
歌德会为此骄傲的
Johann would be very proud.

1285
01:54:32,867 --> 01:54:35,411
你该死在拉齐尔剑下
Now you shall die by Raziel's sword.

1286
01:54:36,412 --> 01:54:37,621
住手！
Stop!

1287
01:54:38,581 --> 01:54:39,665
要么我就丢了它！
Or I'll drop it!

1288
01:54:40,457 --> 01:54:41,667
你不会那么做的
You don't want to do that.

1289
01:54:42,293 --> 01:54:43,627
克拉蕾，别给他
Don't give it to him, Clary.

1290
01:54:51,176 --> 01:54:53,304
你先听我说
I need you to listen to me.

1291
01:54:54,388 --> 01:54:55,639
我是你爸爸
As your father,

1292
01:54:55,723 --> 01:54:57,349
我求你了
I'm begging you.

1293
01:55:03,272 --> 01:55:05,107
要是我爸爸就一定懂我
If you'd been a real dad,

1294
01:55:05,190 --> 01:55:07,818
懂得圣杯在哪里
you'd know me well enough to imagine where the Cup is,

1295
01:55:07,902 --> 01:55:10,529
知道我心底想的地方
where my deepest thoughts are taking it.

1296
01:55:11,822 --> 01:55:14,617
你一点都不懂我
You don't know the first thing about me.

1297
01:55:15,534 --> 01:55:17,328
你不是我爸…
You're not my dad...

1298
01:55:18,704 --> 01:55:20,539
永远不是
And you never will be.

1299
01:55:20,623 --> 01:55:22,875
我保证你不会再见到我
I promise, you'll never have to see me again.

1300
01:55:29,423 --> 01:55:30,633
克拉蕾，谢谢
Thank you, Clary.

1301
01:55:35,262 --> 01:55:38,307
没有圣杯，我们会输的
Without this Cup, we are lost.

1302
01:55:39,266 --> 01:55:40,517
不是“我们”
Not "we."

1303
01:55:42,811 --> 01:55:43,854
是你
You.

1304
01:56:08,796 --> 01:56:09,964
克拉蕾！
Clary!

1305
01:56:13,050 --> 01:56:15,177
- 不！抓住我！  - 决不！
- No! Don't let go! - Never!

1306
01:56:18,305 --> 01:56:19,390
这儿！
Here!

1307
01:57:18,323 --> 01:57:19,783
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

1308
01:57:20,617 --> 01:57:22,119
我不知道
I don't know.

1309
01:58:01,784 --> 01:58:04,411
我知道你之前为什么那样做了
I understand why you did what you did.

1310
01:58:06,663 --> 01:58:08,332
我原谅你
And I forgive you.

1311
01:58:09,708 --> 01:58:11,668
我要你知道
I want you to know,

1312
01:58:13,754 --> 01:58:15,881
我会为你保密
your secret's safe with me.

1313
01:59:09,643 --> 01:59:12,187
她怎么样了？
So, how's she doing?

1314
01:59:12,896 --> 01:59:14,064
情况稳定了
Stable.

1315
01:59:14,731 --> 01:59:16,775
医生不知道她喝过什么
The doctors don't know what she took,

1316
01:59:16,859 --> 01:59:19,069
只能等
so we just have to wait.

1317
01:59:22,739 --> 01:59:24,491
对不起
I'm sorry.

1318
01:59:24,575 --> 01:59:26,535
我觉得我只是一个老古董
I guess I'm an old romantic.

1319
01:59:26,618 --> 01:59:28,829
我总希望当我向某人说
I always hoped that when I finally said

1320
01:59:28,912 --> 01:59:32,082
“我爱你”时，她会说同样的话
"I love you" to someone, she'd say the same thing back.

1321
01:59:32,541 --> 01:59:34,334
那个人会的
And that someone will.

1322
01:59:34,418 --> 01:59:35,752
但愿吧
Yeah, I know.

1323
01:59:44,928 --> 01:59:46,597
你很累了
Hey, you're tired.

1324
01:59:46,680 --> 01:59:49,099
去休息吧，我们会照看好她
Go sleep, we'll take care of her.

1325
01:59:50,267 --> 01:59:51,768
好，抱一个
Yeah, come on.

1326
02:00:43,237 --> 02:00:45,280
我喜欢你收拾这里
I like what you've done with the place.

1327
02:00:45,364 --> 02:00:47,824
我只是耍了些把戏
I've got a few tricks up my sleeve.

1328
02:00:49,618 --> 02:00:51,787
克拉蕾，我们真怕你不会回来了
Clary, we're afraid you're not coming back.

1329
02:00:53,330 --> 02:00:54,915
只是现在跟你作伴真的很难
It's just really hard to be around you right now.

1330
02:00:54,998 --> 02:00:57,000
对我来说也一样
It's hard for me as well.

1331
02:00:58,335 --> 02:01:00,671
但是这不仅仅是我们
But this is about more than us.

1332
02:01:01,964 --> 02:01:04,883
你有不可思议的天赋，我们需要你
You have an incredible gift, and we need you.

1333
02:01:07,970 --> 02:01:09,346
我需要你
I need you.

1334
02:01:10,514 --> 02:01:12,182
我不知道
I just don't know.

1335
02:01:12,849 --> 02:01:15,018
还记得我说过从没见过天使？
Remember when I said I'd never seen an angel?

1336
02:01:19,231 --> 02:01:20,691
我撒谎了
Well, I lied.

1337
02:01:30,242 --> 02:01:32,244
你是我见过最勇敢的凡人
You're still the bravest mundane I've ever met.

1338
02:01:36,707 --> 02:01:38,375
我可不是凡人
I'm not a mundane.

1339
02:01:41,003 --> 02:01:42,170
等等，杰斯！
Wait, Jace!

1340
02:01:46,508 --> 02:01:47,759
慢慢来啊
You took your time.

1341
02:01:54,725 --> 02:01:56,643
你说过你需要我
You said you needed me.

1342
02:02:01,606 --> 02:02:03,066
你该好好保存它
You should keep that safe.

1343
02:02:03,150 --> 02:02:04,276
我会的
Yeah.

1344
02:02:05,902 --> 02:02:07,612
我可以抱着你吗…
Is it okay if I...

1345
02:02:08,572 --> 02:02:09,990
我能…
Do I...

1346
02:02:10,073 --> 02:02:12,242
- 这样可以吗…  - 没关系
- Is it okay if I... - Yeah.

1347
02:02:15,495 --> 02:02:17,748
听着，克拉蕾，我不相信它
Look, Clary, I don't believe it.

1348
02:02:17,831 --> 02:02:19,541
这似乎不是真的，不在我的心里
It doesn't feel like the truth, not in my heart.

1349
02:02:21,168 --> 02:02:24,254
我只是不懂如何去面对这个世界
I just don't know how to look at the world anymore.

1350
02:02:24,338 --> 02:02:27,132
我看不到街道，红绿灯和车
I don't see streets and traffic lights and cars.

1351
02:02:27,215 --> 02:02:29,176
眼前只是邪灵和天使
I see demons and angels.

1352
02:02:30,135 --> 02:02:31,136
一切都变了
Everything's different.

1353
02:02:31,219 --> 02:02:33,013
世界还是一样的
The world's the same.

1354
02:02:33,930 --> 02:02:36,224
你才是变了的那个
You're the one who's different.

1355
02:02:42,439 --> 02:02:44,066
你还记得霍奇说的吗？
Don't you remember what Hodge said?

1356
02:02:44,149 --> 02:02:45,359
什么？
What?

1357
02:02:45,442 --> 02:02:47,110
所以故事都是真的
All the stories are true.

1358
02:03:00,587 --> 02:03:03,158
感谢观影
